This Software is a CONTROL INTERFACE for offensive security tools. It does NOT
itself exploit vulnerabilities, phish users, or establish command-and-control
channels — the underlying tools do. Nevertheless, wrapping those tools behind
an LLM-callable interface dramatically lowers the barrier to misuse.

You agree, as a condition of using the Software, that you will ONLY use it:

  1. Against systems you OWN, or
  2. Against systems for which you possess PRIOR WRITTEN AUTHORIZATION
     from the lawful owner (e.g. a signed pentest scope, a published bug-bounty
     program in-scope target, a sanctioned red-team engagement, or a CTF range),
     AND
  3. In compliance with ALL applicable laws, including but not limited to:
       * US: Computer Fraud and Abuse Act (18 U.S.C. §1030)
       * EU: Directive 2013/40/EU, GDPR
       * China: 中华人民共和国网络安全法, 刑法第 285/286 条
       * UK: Computer Misuse Act 1990
       * and any jurisdiction where you or the target reside.

